{"tid":1520471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國安顧問：中國匿蹤戰機 偷美F-35技術","createTime":"2019-08-30T21:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:53:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb8d433af891283367aeeba10a0af5b65b66d9d","tid":1520471,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:37:01.000Z","msg":"美國安顧問：中國匿蹤戰機 偷美F-35技術<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6477825/article-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%89%e9%a1%a7%e5%95%8f%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%8c%bf%e8%b9%a4%e6%88%b0%e6%a9%9f-%e5%81%b7%e7%be%8ef-35%e6%8a%80%e8%a1%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6477825%2Farticle-%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25ae%2589%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%2595%258f%25ef%25bc%259a%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%258c%25bf%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e6%2588%25b0%25e6%25a9%259f-%25e5%2581%25b7%25e7%25be%258ef-35%25e6%258a%2580%25e8%25a1%2593%2F&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a11f7dd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6477825/article-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%89%e9%a1%a7%e5%95%8f%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%8c%bf%e8%b9%a4%e6%88%b0%e6%a9%9f-%e5%81%b7%e7%be%8ef-35%e6%8a%80%e8%a1%93/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問波頓（John Bolton）日前稱中國的第五代戰機與美國戰機酷似，指控中國竊取美製匿蹤戰機F-35的研發計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">俄羅斯「衛星通信社」（Sputnik）報導，波頓在烏克蘭首都基輔出席一場記者會時說：「中國第5代戰機看起來像極F-35，這是因為他們做出來的就是F-35的翻版，不過是竊取技術。」<br />\n<br />\n波頓聲稱，剽竊F-35戰機是中國數十年來竊取美國智慧財產的例證，「美國與中國目前在貿易上歧見甚深。這不光是關於兩國間的進、出口失衡&hellip;‥，而是有關為何會存在失衡的根本原因」。</span><br />\n<br />\n「今日俄羅斯」（RT）則大酸波頓指出，多年來中國一直是美國指控竊取技術的頭號目標，包括提到F-35，但波頓其實更該看看別國「竊密」作品。<br />\n<br />\n因為按他的說法，近期包括英國航太系統公司（BAE）推出、預計2030年代中葉服役的第6代戰機「暴風」（Tempest），看起來也跟F-35如出一轍；由德、法兩國今年6月推出的新世代戰機計畫，同樣也像極F-35；土耳其推出的TF-X匿蹤戰機式樣，應也是剽竊疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n今日俄羅斯指出，嚴格來說，讓戰機不易被雷達捕獲的匿蹤概念，有特定的氣動外型要求，因而使飛機設計人員某種程度都會做類似設計方向，單就飛機外觀就來指控產業剽竊不無疑問，況且現代飛機比的全是內部系統，而非數十年下來早已成基本ABC的氣動外型。"},{"pid":"180cfcb10b6833fe92bf99636d9c9847ba9aec21","tid":1520471,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:37:11.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=9a49b6be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f349e312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=04490ed7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=55925942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike929